備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 畢業生應具備科技人文素養、醫學資訊工程倫理與終身學習的態度
 graduates should equip with the attitude of technological/cultural literacy, medical informatics ethics, and life-long learning
□ 畢業生應具備專業外語能力及良好國際觀
 graduates should equip with both professional foreign language proficiency and excellent global view
 

核心能力 Competence
□ 畢業生應具備資訊專業知識與研究之能力
 graduates should equip with the capability of professional knowledge and research in informatics
□ 畢業生應具備醫學資訊知識及應用之能力
 graduates should equip with the capability of knowledge and applications in medical informatics
□ 畢業生應具備醫學資訊領域獨立發掘問題、策劃實驗、解決問題之能力
 graduates should equip with the medical informatics ability to identify problems independently, to conduct experiments, and to solve problems
□ 畢業生應具備應用資訊科技解決醫學資訊問題的能力
 graduates should equip with the ability to apply information technology in solving problems in medical informatics
□ 畢業生應具備醫學資訊領域整合與創新思考之能力
 graduates should equip with the medical informatics capability on the integration and innovative planning
□ 畢業生應具備專業簡報及論文撰寫之能力
 graduates should equip with the ability in professional presentation and thesis writing
□ 畢業生應具備良好溝通協調與團隊合作之能力
 graduates should equip with fair ability in communication, coordination, and team-work collaboration
 

課程概述 Course Description
 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    奠定學生電生理學基礎並熟悉電生理學實驗技術，使學生日後從事電生理相關研究工作可以順利進行。引起學生對神經科學的興趣，建立神經科學相關研究領域之基本知識。    

